Hello Maria,

Language is not easy.  The phrase "list all the factors of 2 within 10"  doesn't have a very 
clear meaning to me, particularly the "within."

We know that 10 = 2*5.  It has, I think, one factor of 2.  10 would not be included,  
because it is not a "factor of 2."


